<br />Yeah, I was going to point out that 7 and 8 were already released after X, 9 isn't the only one out of place. Seems to me like they skipped to 10 because they wanted to do something special for the SNES, but they kept the old numbering going as well, until 9, when they finally closed the gap.

		

