		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />This has been argued on forums since time immemorial. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />
<br />
<br />I'm pretty certain X was never supposed to signify ten, considering we have X-2 instead of XI or eleven.  It signifies a split in the series rather than a sequel.  This is further confirmed by the fact that 9 does not segue into X in any way.  Theoretically there could be a Megaman 10 and it would make perfect sense.  In fact I hope they do that, to put to rest the talk about X being ten.

		

